### HYMN LXVII

#### A prayer for long life

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_1906701">1</span></span>A hundred
autumns may we see.  
<span class="margnote"><span id="an_1906702">2</span></span>A hundred
autumns may we live.  
<span class="margnote"><span id="an_1906703">3</span></span>A hundred
autumns may we know.  
<span class="margnote"><span id="an_1906704">4</span></span>A hundred
autumns may we grow.  
<span class="margnote"><span id="an_1906705">5</span></span>A hundred
autumns may we thrive.  
<span class="margnote"><span id="an_1906706">6</span></span>A hundred
autumns may we be.  
<span class="margnote"><span id="an_1906707">7</span></span>A hundred
autumns may we bide.  
<span class="margnote"><span id="an_1906708">8</span></span>A hundred,
yea, and even more.

